high_descs: Go left and stand in front of the gray trash can left of the counter.
Pick the apple up out of the trash can.
Go right and turn to face the sink.
Put the apple in the microwave and shut the door and then open it and take the apple out.
Go left and turn to face the trash can.
Put the apple in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a warmed apple in the trash can.

high_descs: Turn left, go forward to the wall, turn right, then go towards the trash bin.
Take the apple from the trash bin.
Turn right, go forward, then turn left at the sink.
Heat the apple in the microwave, above the sink.
Go left, go forward, then turn right to face the trash bin.
Put the apple in the trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm apple in the trash.

high_descs: Move to the bin on the right past the sink
Pick up an apple from the bin
Move to the sink to the right of you
Heat up the apple in the microwave
Move to the bin to the left
Put the apple in the bin
anns.task_desc: Put a heated apple in the bin.
